title: Watch live: President Trump announces Supreme Court pick
text:
Jan. 31, 2017, 4:56 p.m. 
This is our look at President Trump's administration and the rest of Washington: Homeland Security secretary says countries on banned list "may not be taken off anytime soon" Supreme Court pick coming tonight Acting attorney general fired by Trump Trump orders agencies to cut back on regulations White House clarifies how new immigration policy affects green-card holders Supreme Court Jan. 31, 2017, 4:56 p.m. Watch live: President Trump announces Supreme Court pick Latest updates
